<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Health Check OpenShift del Cluster Filice.eu</title>
    <style>
        /* Bootstrap-like styles */
        .table {
            width: 100%;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            color: #212529;
        }

        .table th,
        .table td {
            padding: 0.75rem;
            vertical-align: top;
            border-top: 1px solid #dee2e6;
        }

        .table thead th {
            vertical-align: bottom;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #dee2e6;
        }

        .table tbody + tbody {
            border-top: 2px solid #dee2e6;
        }

        .table .table {
            background-color: #fff;
        }

        .table-sm th,
        .table-sm td {
            padding: 0.3rem;
        }

        .table-bordered {
            border: 1px solid #dee2e6;
        }

        .table-bordered th,
        .table-bordered td {
            border: 1px solid #dee2e6;
        }

        /* Additional styles */
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }

        p {
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        /* Add any additional styles you need */

    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <p>Tale report viene generato da un playbook Ansible scritto da Alberto Filice insieme a ChatGPT.</p>
    <p>Dopo diverse correzioni e fix, abbiamo creato un playbook che possa verificare lo stato del cluster, di ODF, e lo spazio rimanente sia di ODF e sia dei nodi.</p><br>
    <table class="table table-bordered">
        <thead>
            <tr>
                <th>Nome controllo</th>
                <th>Stato</th>
            </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
            {% for check in checks %}
            <tr>
                <td>{{ check.name }}</td>
                <td>{{ check.status }}</td>
            </tr>
            {% endfor %}
        </tbody>
    </table>
</body>
</html>
